{"tid":2408711,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"月入好撚多，想養返幾隻熊看門口","createTime":"2021-02-15T08:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T09:22:36.000Z","uid":47374,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f2e92d1a1be7b31399629855ca0a968d8e7f9b1a","tid":2408711,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:02:46.000Z","msg":"等唔到飛機了，等唔到飛機了！！<br />\n想行路去俄羅斯馴伏返幾隻熊睇住啲錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8KpZyr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8KpZyr.jpg&h=8f206344&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母順便溝返個俄羅斯人類老母<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZoBQFC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZoBQFC.jpg&h=b02fb19f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馴伏多隻俄佬豹<br />\n廢事佢地唔小心行咗去支那俾人食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SzDqJ1M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSzDqJ1M.jpg&h=80fcd544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係馴獸師之王！<br />\n屌你老母！我就係馴獸師之王！<br />\n走呀西伯利亞虎！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KcbPrfR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKcbPrfR.jpg&h=9e17b8d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時計劃係咁，行得通嘅話再游去南美，<br />\n說服啲美洲虎嚟我屋企<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/paFMtu4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpaFMtu4.jpg&h=ea27bc41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06d0b981d086d4c3fa014991786eeb02487b760f","tid":2408711,"uid":69866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:04:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">無是咁的，零分重作</span>"},{"pid":"619ffd8ac4a9d5b1f913afe753678590a827333f","tid":2408711,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06d0b981d086d4c3fa014991786eeb02487b760f","tid":2408711,"uid":69866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:04:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">無是咁的，零分重作</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:06:25.000Z","msg":"計